<h2 id="pagetitle">Safe Online Buying Guide</h2>
<p>
Here at LLC Ltd, we are the sole importers and distributors of Lafuma Furniture for the UK market. Our website (www.lafuma.co.uk) is designed not only to give information about the <a href="index.php">current Lafuma range</a> available in the UK, but also gives you the opportunity to purchase these goods online directly. We also have a range of designs exclusive only to our website. These can be found by going to the <a href="index.php?p=products&amp;cat=10">Special Offers</a> page. 
</p>
<p>
You can be assured that www.lafuma.co.uk is a secure website, with up to date security certificates provided from Comodo. For details of how we use any of your credentials you enter when purchasing from our online shop, please read our <a href="index.php?p=privacy">Privacy Policy</a>. Any payment made online with us is authorised through a third party known as <a href="http://www.sagepay.com/" target="_blank">SagePay</a>. 
</p>
<p>
Unfortunately, we are aware of certain internet retailers who sell Lafuma products, despite the fact that they are not authorised to do so. We recommend that you do not use these sites. If an issue arises that you are unable to resolve with the site you purchased the product, then we will also not be in a position to help you further. We recommend only purchasing from either our website, or the websites &amp; shops listed in our <a href="index.php?p=dealers">Local Stockists</a> section. 
</p>
<p>
Whenever you purchase online, it is important that you remain cautious of your security, and take all reasonable steps to stay safe. Read through any websites terms and conditions carefully before committing to any purchase, as well as any returns procedures they may have set in place. Also, please make sure that you are able to find the companies contact details before you make a purchase. This is important as you may need to contact the website after your purchase has been made. For further advice on how to stay safe online please see the Government backed <a href="https://www.getsafeonline.org/" target="_blank">Stay Safe Online</a> website.
</p>